%N A015777 Inverse of 1768th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015777 Periodic with period length 1768. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015777 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015777/b015777.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015777 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1768.
